PrimaryStyle|Virginia Tech Hokies|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''Tied 11\u201311'''<br/><small>(VT wins tiebreaker)<br>UVA led 2\u20131</small>\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Tech Hokies|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''VT 12\u00bd\u20138\u00bd'''<br/><small>Tied 2\u20132</small>\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA 12\u00bd\u20139\u00bd'''<br/><small>UVA leads 3\u20132</small>\n|-\n! Sport !! 2014\u201315<ref name=\"clash_results\">{{cite web |title=2014\u20132015 Schedule/Results |url=http://www.thecommonwealthclash.com/gameday/index.php |publisher=The Commonwealth Clash |accessdate=28 November 2014}}</ref>\n! 2015\u201316\n! 2016\u201317\n! 2017\u201318\n! 2018\u201319\n|-\n| style=\"background: #f6f6f6;\" |[[College soccer|Men's Soccer]] \n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"background: #cccccc; color:#222222\" | '''Halved'''\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"background: #cccccc; color:#222222\" | '''Halved'''\n|-\n| style=\"background: #f6f6f6;\" |[[Women's football (soccer)|Women's Soccer]]\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"background: #cccccc; color:#222\" | ''Did Not Play''\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"background: #cccccc; color:#222\" | ''Did Not Play''\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Tech Hokies|border=0|color=white}};\" | '''VT'''\n|-\n| style=\"background: #f6f6f6;\" |[[Cross country running|Men's Cross Country]]\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|border=0|color=white}}\" | '''UVA'''\n| style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Virginia Cavaliers|bo