ies flock to Libya raising fears of prolonged war &#124; World news |publisher=The Guardian |date= |accessdate=2020-01-15}}</ref>\n| strength2         = {{flagicon|Libya}}{{flagicon image|The emblem on the passport of Libya.svg|border=no}} 5,000 total<ref name=\"bastion\"/><ref name=\"SANA_WhoWhom_Tripoli\">{{cite web | last1 =Lacher | first1 =Wolfram | author1link = Wolfram Lacher | title= Who is fighting whom in Tripoli? How the 2019 civil war is transforming Libya's military landscape | website = Security Assessment in North Africa Briefing Paper |trans-title = <!-- trans-title is the English translation --> |year = 2019 | url = http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/fileadmin/docs/T-Briefing-Papers/SAS-SANA-BP-Tripoli-2019.pdf | accessdate = 11 November 2019 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20191110232900/http://www.smallarmssurvey.org/fileadmin/docs/T-Briefing-Papers/SAS-SANA-BP-Tripoli-2019.pdf |archivedate= 10 November 2019 |url-status=live <!-- live|dead|unfit|usurped -->}}</ref>\n*3,000 (in Tripoli) \n*2,000 (in Tripoli's surroundings)\n{{flagicon|Syrian opposition}} 5,050 (March 2020) <ref name=\"Guardian_2kSNA_helping_GNA\" /><ref name=\"Xinhuasyrianrebels\"/><ref>http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=159958</ref>\n{{Flagicon|Turkey}} 35 advisors<ref name=\"Guardian_2kSNA_helping_GNA\" />\n| casualties1       = {{flagicon|Libya}}{{flagicon image|Libyan COA used by Haftar.png|70px|border=no}} Unknown killed<br>{{flagicon|Libya}}{{flagicon image|Libyan COA used by Haftar.png|70px|border=no}} 1 MiG-21MF lost<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/north-africa/2019/04/14/Haftar-forces-fighter-jet-downed-near-libya-capital-says-unity-government.html|title=Haftar forces' fighter jet downed near Libya capital, says unity government|website=english.alarabiya.net|accessdate=15 April 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20190415-libya-commander-haftar-egypts-sisi-fighting-tripoli|title=Libyan commander Haftar meets Egypt's Sisi as fig